  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300159706_36_4924-4964",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "4924-4964",
      "markText": "“做好储蓄”“不乱消费”和“低欲望生活”是日本现在年轻人应对经济下行的三件法宝。",
      "totalCount": 7360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300159706&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=4924&rangeEnd=4964",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/77d32440813aba4e2g01644a?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=4924&rangeEnd=4964"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300159706_32_5125-5175",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "5125-5175",
      "markText": "日本将海量资金用于救助企业而不是用来发展科技，而这不仅连累了金融体系，也断送了日本高科技产业的未来。",
      "totalCount": 7327,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300159706&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=5125&rangeEnd=5175",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/77d32440813aba4e2g01644a?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=5125&rangeEnd=5175"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300159706_33_4557-4636",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "4557-4636",
      "markText": "1992年至1995年间，面对大学生就业的严峻形势，日本政府推出了“乡村分流”与“研究生扩招”两项举措，旨在尽量延缓大学生进入就业市场的时间，以缓解就业压力。",
      "totalCount": 6816,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300159706&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=4557&rangeEnd=4636",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/77d32440813aba4e2g01644a?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=4557&rangeEnd=4636"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300159706_52_569-604",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "569-604",
      "markText": "潮水退去时，沙滩上留下的贝壳纹路各异，却都藏着同一片大海的呜咽与回响。",
      "totalCount": 6678,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300159706&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=569&rangeEnd=604",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/77d32440813aba4e2g01644a?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=569&rangeEnd=604"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300159706_33_396-486",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "396-486",
      "markText": "他们出生于20世纪70年代的日本婴儿潮时期，学生时代的他们见证了日本80年代的经济腾飞，却在毕业后迎面撞上90年代无止境的经济衰退。最终，他们成为日本收入最低、结婚率也最低的群体。",
      "totalCount": 5290,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300159706&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=396&rangeEnd=486",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/77d32440813aba4e2g01644a?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=396&rangeEnd=486"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300159706_36_5908-5933",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "5908-5933",
      "markText": "但却无人告诉他们：其实不是他们错了，而是社会病了。",
      "totalCount": 5194,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300159706&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=5908&rangeEnd=5933",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/77d32440813aba4e2g01644a?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=5908&rangeEnd=5933"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300159706_30_2473-2502",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "2473-2502",
      "markText": "世界上只有一种英雄主义，就是看清生活的真相之后依然热爱它。",
      "totalCount": 5072,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300159706&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=2473&rangeEnd=2502",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/77d32440813aba4e2g01644a?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=2473&rangeEnd=2502"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300159706_32_8857-8930",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "8857-8930",
      "markText": "后来，泡沫经济时期毕业的大学生被称为暖春一代，而泡沫后毕业的大学生则被称为寒冬一代。两代大学生仅仅因为读书时间的不同，就面临着两种截然不同的人生。",
